{"tid":370552,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"gto失樂園","createTime":"2017-08-23T05:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T06:44:40.000Z","uid":129474,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"73f7c9dd8d9f45eb7d613a2cff524eff6eb6dada","tid":370552,"uid":129474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T05:56:18.000Z","msg":"有無巴打追開呢套？今日打風一口氣睇晒，發覺同之前嘅gto好大分別，啲畫功好似唔同晒，故事又無以前咁細膩，無本傳同湘南14日咁好睇"},{"pid":"aafee38e769ae4b7b0bc10fb402ced7731176914","tid":370552,"uid":2223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:08:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無巴打追開呢套？今日打風一口氣睇晒，發覺同之前嘅gto好大分別，啲畫功好似唔同晒，故事又無以前咁細膩，無本傳同湘南14日咁好睇</blockquote><br />\n仲要一d都唔好笑"},{"pid":"9b07de2d561fddb99afd60f22a079d3f3f9281ed","tid":370552,"uid":38271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:09:40.000Z","msg":"14日後無GTO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n畫風改到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b16a120bbbe11101ae7f3d05cd957a754ef50a","tid":370552,"uid":129474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:12:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無巴打追開呢套？今日打風一口氣睇晒，發覺同之前嘅gto好大分別，啲畫功好似唔同晒，故事又無以前咁細膩，無本傳同湘南14日咁好睇</blockquote><br />\n仲要一d都唔好笑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪技窮，好多笑位都笑唔出，好似嚟嚟去去都係嗰啲<br />\n好掛住菊地同麗美"},{"pid":"a04deb0c4a5e2bf87ed685f00e289807764721f4","tid":370552,"uid":129474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:14:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>14日後無GTO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n畫風改到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係，14日帶出個家暴社會議題好好，成個故事好細緻<br />\n而家失樂園成日都好似跳線咁，而且啲故事間無聯繫，好似sharp cut咁，無本傳嗰種整體感"},{"pid":"bc45c754ea9f0bd366e11c3dd1682d127c8ec096","tid":370552,"uid":9247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T03:20:16.000Z","msg":"放棄左"},{"pid":"223cd9854dde7ffc1eaf0aed2cf32072ce029112","tid":370552,"uid":33104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T03:29:15.000Z","msg":"班入面d學生，大多數出一個故事就唔見左，無左無印果時，成班同學果種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cac5e5eec117932477f053e9da7f0e9b07e6286","tid":370552,"uid":2386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T05:26:30.000Z","msg":"湘南14日都麻麻哋<br />\n呢套直頭棄咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉同龍珠一樣自己拆咗自己招牌"},{"pid":"08940fe18823519bb49cfc0807b3b6cb6c5543d4","tid":370552,"uid":129474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T06:22:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班入面d學生，大多數出一個故事就唔見左，無左無印果時，成班同學果種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個point好岩，校園漫畫如果無學生之間個互動，同埋定時出場撐下的話讀者好難記得<br />\n<br />\n本傳吉川同上原條線我好鍾意"},{"pid":"39dd4c705ec9526ca0d1be3ddff8d62b88d00571","tid":370552,"uid":129474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T06:23:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>湘南14日都麻麻哋<br />\n呢套直頭棄咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉同龍珠一樣自己拆咗自己招牌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n14日當外傳睇ok，始終無本傳嗰種味道"},{"pid":"4362ccc52a5c4ee96700f893b281af40ee892b66","tid":370552,"uid":99960,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T06:34:34.000Z","msg":"睇過幾集冇睇同本傳真係差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c70bca347d84efeb9914c456a0d622feb130016","tid":370552,"uid":129474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T06:44:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇過幾集冇睇同本傳真係差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打鬥場面都無本傳咁好睇"}]}